I halved the sauce and included it in with 7 large chicken legs (which is all that fit in my roasting pan) and they were done before the additional 15 minutes of cooking time suggested (basted every 15 min. or so). The thickened sauce in the pan was more than adequate for serving alongside the chicken instead of the 3/4 cup uncooked sauce as directed in the recipe and most of the alcohol in the wine is cooked off. My family really enjoys this dish!

